            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p><g type="cross"/>
               <lb/>
               <choice><orig>Μνημῖ<lb break="no"/>αν</orig><reg>μνημεῖον</reg></choice>
                    <choice><orig>Θειώ<lb break="no"/>νη</orig><reg>Θεώνης</reg></choice> Σαμιρ<lb break="no"/>άββου, <choice><orig>παυ<lb break="no"/>σαμένη</orig><reg>παυσαμένης</reg></choice> ἐτ<lb break="no"/>ῶν <space unit="character" quantity="1"/>
                    <num value="25">κε</num>,<lb/>ἔτους <num value="287">σπζ</num>
               <lb/>
               <expan><abbr>μη</abbr><ex>νὸς</ex></expan>
                    <choice><orig>Ἀπελλέ<lb break="no"/>ου</orig><reg>Ἀπελλαίου</reg></choice>
                    <num value="5">ε</num>. <choice><orig>Θάρσι</orig><reg>θάρσει</reg></choice>
               <lb/>
               <choice><orig>οὐδὶς</orig><reg>οὐδεις</reg></choice> ἀθά<lb break="no"/>νατος.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Monument of Theone, (daughter) of Samirabbos, who died (at the age) of 25 years,
                    in (the) year 287, on the 5th (day) of (the) month Apellaios. Be of good cheer,
                    no one (is) immortal.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p/>
            </div>
